Update [dbo].[Teacher]
Set[Description]= N' <p>I am a PhD of Comparative Linguistics in Department of English Linguistics at University of Social Sciences and Humanities – Vietnam National University Ho Chi Minh City.</p>
                    <p>Education is the mission that I have done. I have attached a full life with the word "Education", so even though in any circumstance I always want to bring education to everyone.</p>
                    <p>I had a lot of years in education and I think they need to do more now to be able to bring education to everyone.</p>
                    <p>Teaching through many universities I feel that students now are less confident in himself and his destiny betting on a scalar.</p>
                    <p>I hope the courses that I was directly taught will help students better Vietnam.</p>'
